Judd Green https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Judd_Green 0 Judd Green (1866–1932) was a British film actor of the silent era. He was sometimes credited as R. Judd Green. He was born in Portsmouth, Hampshire in 1866 and made his first screen appearance in 1914. Judd_Green ( 1866 – 1932 ) was a_British_film_actor of the_silent_era .
